           "rendered": "\n<h2 style=\"text-align: right;\">(&#1575;&#1604;&#1602;&#1585;&#1570;&#1606; (&#1776;&#1778;:&#1778;&#1778;&#1778;</h2>\n<p><div class=\"wwm_socialshare_imagewrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4842\" src=\"https://quranicquotes.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/quran_urdu_baqrah_222.png\" alt=\"Quranic Quotes Urdu #248\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" srcset=\"https://quranicquotes.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/quran_urdu_baqrah_222.png 2000w, https://quranicquotes.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/quran_urdu_baqrah_222-744x744.png 744w, https://quranicquotes.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/quran_urdu_baqrah_222-1200x1200.png 1200w, https://quranicquotes.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/quran_urdu_baqrah_222-420x420.png 420w, https://quranicquotes.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/quran_urdu_baqrah_222-768x768.png 768w, https://quranicquotes.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/quran_urdu_baqrah_222-1536x1536.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></div></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\">&#1575;&#1585;&#1583;&#1608;</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">&#1740;&#1602;&#1740;&#1606;&#1575;&#1575;&#1604;&#1604;&#1729; &#1578;&#1593;&#1575;&#1604;&#1740;&#1648; &#1576;&#1729;&#1578; &#1578;&#1608;&#1576;&#1729; &#1705;&#1585;&#1606;&#1746; &#1608;&#1575;&#1604;&#1608;&#1722; &#1575;&#1608;&#1585; &#1576;&#1729;&#1578; &#1662;&#1575;&#1705; &#1585;&#1729;&#1606;&#1746; &#1608;&#1575;&#1604;&#1608;&#1722; &#1587;&#1746; &#1605;&#1581;&#1576;&#1578; &#1705;&#1585;&#1578;&#1575; &#1729;&#1746;</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>English</h3>\n<blockquote><p>They ask you &#761;O Prophet&#762; about menstruation. Say, &ldquo;Beware of its harm! So keep away, and do not have intercourse with your wives during their monthly cycles until they are purified. When they purify themselves, then you may approach them in the manner specified by Allah. Surely Allah loves those who always turn to Him in repentance and those who purify themselves.&rdquo;</p></blockquote>\n<ul class=\"wwm_social_share wwm_top_right\"><li class=\"wwm_facebook\"></li><li class=\"wwm_twitter\"></li><li class=\"wwm_pinit\"></li><li class=\"wwm_tumblr\"></li></ul><input type=\"hidden\" id=\"wwm_mode\" value=\"1\"/>",
